My new bride and I (both 59 years of age) had the most incredible honeymoon in New York
staying at the Hotel Iroquois
From check
to the quality of the room
to the helpfulness of the concierges
to the level of service
we could not have been more pleased with our stay
The decor of the room was great
The amenities in the room were thoughtful
The staff was attentive and extremely helpful
The recommendations by the concierge were terrific
